{"word":"H7364 - רָחַץ - râchats - raw-khats' - Bathe","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָחַץ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>râchats"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>raw-khats'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Bathe"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கழுவு, ஸ்நானம் பண்ணு, முழுகு, சுத்திசெய், குளி, கழுவப்படு, குளிப்பாட்டு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to wash, to wash off, to wash away, to bathe"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to wash, to wash off, to wash away"},{"paragraph":"2) to wash, to bathe (oneself)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Pual) to be washed"},{"paragraph":"c) (Hithpael) to wash oneself"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>lave</i> (the whole or a part of the thing): - bathe (self), wash (self)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7364 - רָחַץ - râchats - raw-khats'/7364\">H7364</a>, <a href=\"#/H7366 - רַחַץ - rachats - rakh'-ats/7366\">H7366</a>, <a href=\"#/H7367 - רַחְצָה - rachtsâh - rakh-tsaw'/7367\">H7367</a>"}]}